                 \n                        Not all items sold on store.mopar.com are shippable.\n                        Promotion valid only on online orders of shippable items with a minimum\n                        order value of $214+, made from <strong>02/14/2026 through 02/28/2026</strong>,\n                        fulfilled by a participating U.S. Mopar Dealer. Offer code automatically\n                        applied at online checkout. Promotion covers up to <strong>$50 of the total\n                        shipping fee</strong>; any remaining shipping fee balance is the sole\n                        responsibility of the customer. No cash value. Void where prohibited.\n                        Other restrictions may apply. Contact participating U.S. Mopar Dealer\n                        for details.\n                      \n                    </span>\n                  </span>\n                </p>\n                <a href=\"javascript:openVehiclePicker();\" class=\"themeNewBannerSliderButton\">\n                  Shop Now\n                </a>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"themeNewBannerSliderItem\">\n            <a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#creditCardPromoModal\">\n                <div class=\"themeNewBannerSliderBox\">\n                    <div class=\"themeNewBannerSliderImg\">\n                        <img src=\"https://rparts-sites.s3.amazonaws.com/21ebc25a592052689288153b3e3fb858/design/new-home/slider/Mopar_75LTO_Banner_978x700-EO-n.webp\" fetchpriority=\"high\" alt=\"MOPAR Authentic Parts & Accessories\">\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </a>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"themeNewBannerSliderItem\">\n            <div class=\"themeNewBannerSliderBox\">\n                <a href=\"rho-magnaflow-exhaust/?mt1carousel\">\n                    <div class=\"themeNewBannerSliderBox\">\n                        <div class=\"themeNewBAnnerSliderContent\">\n                            <div class=\"themeNewBannerSliderContentBox\">\n                                <h4>RHO Exhaust Kits</h4>\n                                <p class=\"themeNewBannerSliderText\">\n                                    MagnaFlow RAM RHO xMOD and SPEQ Series Cat-Back Performance Exhaust\n                                </p>\n                                <p class=\"themeNewBannerSliderButton\">\n                                    Shop Now\n                                </p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"themeNewBannerSliderImg\">\n                            <img src=\"https://rparts-sites.s3.amazonaws.com/21ebc25a592052689288153b3e3fb858/design/new-home/slider/rho-exhaust-tile_.webp\" fetchpriority=\"high\" alt=\"RAM RHO Cat-Back Performance Exhaust\">\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </a>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"themeNewBannerSliderItem\">\n            <div class=\"themeNewBannerSliderBox\">\n                <a href=\"https://store.mopar.com/jeep-wrangler-catalog?mt1carousel\">\n                    <div class=\"themeNewBannerSliderBox\">\n                        <div class=\"themeNewBAnnerSliderContent\">\n                            <div class=\"themeNewBannerSliderContentBox\">\n                                <h4>Jeep Wrangler Interactive Catalog</h4>\n                                <p class=\"themeNewBannerSliderText\">\n                                    An immersive catalog featuring top selling accessories in an interactive experience.\n                                </p>\n                                <p class=\"themeNewBannerSliderButton\">\n                                    Shop Now\n                                </p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"themeNewBannerSliderImg\">\n                            <img src=\"https://rparts-sites.s3.amazonaws.com/21ebc25a592052689288153b3e3fb858/design/new-home/slider/banner_wrangler_.webp\" fetchpriority=\"high\" alt=\"Jeep Wrangler Interactive Catalog\">\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </a>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"themeNewBannerSliderItem\">\n            <a href=\"/affiliated-accessories/?mt1carousel\">\n                <div class=\"themeNewBannerSliderBox\">\n                    <div class=\"themeNewBannerSliderImg\">\n                        <img src=\"https://rparts-sites.s3.amazonaws.com/21ebc25a592052689288153b3e3fb858/design/new-home/slider/square_1a_.webp\" fetchpriority=\"high\" alt=\"MOPAR Authentic Parts & Accessories\">\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"themeNewBAnnerSliderContent\">\n                        <div class=\"themeNewBannerSliderContentBox\">\n                            <h4>Mopar<sub>®</sub> Affiliated Accessories</h4>\n                            <p class=\"themeNewBannerSliderText\">\n                                <strong>Partnered with 30+ trusted brands</strong> to offer top accessories and customization options for your vehicle.\n                            </p>\n                            <p class=\"themeNewBannerSliderButton\">\n                                Shop Now\n                            </p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </a>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"themeNewBannerSliderItem\">\n            <a href=\"bproauto?mt1carousel\">\n                <div class=\"themeNewBannerSliderBox\">\n                    <div class=\"themeNewBAnnerSliderContent\">\n                        <div class=\"themeNewBannerSliderContentBox\">\n                            <h4>BPROAUTO PARTS</h4>\n                            <p class=\"themeNewBannerSliderText\">\n           